《'''火线警告'''》（{{lang|en|Burn Notice}}）是一部由Matt Nix创造，[[杰弗里·多诺万|杰弗里·多诺万]]、[[Gabrielle_Anwar|Gabrielle Anwar]]、[[Bruce_Campbell|Bruce Campbell]]和[[Sharon_Gless|Sharon Gless]]出演的[[美国|美国]][[连续剧|连续剧]]。<ref name="NYT1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/28/arts/television/28tvcol.html?pagewanted=all |title=New York Times: What's on Tonight |access-date=2009-03-07 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629084517/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/28/arts/television/28tvcol.html?pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>这部连续剧中2007年6月28日在[[USA_Network|USA Network]]首播。''Burn Notice''在2008年10月9日签订了第三季16集的合同。<ref>[http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i69c4daba6cf2b7e5d60d9a2349884352 Hollywoodreporter.com] (subscription access)</ref>

这部连续剧的标志口号是:
* ''Spies don't get fired, they get burned.''
* ''Sun. Surf. Espionage.''

